Package: dosbox-frontend
Version: 1.0.0
Section: games
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, dosbox
Maintainer: MatTech <user@example.com>
Description: DOSBox Frontend with easy floppy image management
 A GTK3 frontend for DOSBox that makes it easy to manage and mount
 floppy disk images (.img, .ima, .vfd, .flp). Features include:
  - One-click DOSBox launch
  - Floppy image library with drag-and-drop support
  - Mount images as drive A: or B:
  - Quick Access panel for recently used images
  - Create blank floppy images (FAT12 formatted)
  - Persistent settings
